data.description: NEWLY IMPROVED PRICE! This 4/4.5/2 BEAUTIFUL COUNTRY CHARMER complete with in-ground pool and spa, bonus room, and workshop ON NEARLY 5 ACRES with NO HOA is what dreams are made of! Highlighted by its ever-desirable front porch, this nicely maintained home welcomes you into its grand living area, comfortably met by the warmth of the cozy wood fireplace and natural lighting exuded from the adorned dormer windows and French doors. Overlooking the picturesque property in nearly every room, continue your tour towards the timeless kitchen, 4 spacious bedrooms complete with personal en-suites in each, expansive bonus room, indoor laundry area, and pool and pool deck with newly replaced pump and filtration system! A large workshop, shed, and chicken coop also lay on the property waiting for you to make your farm dreams a reality for your horses, toys, and feathery friends! Nestled peacefully between Inverness and Brooksville for all your shopping and recreational needs, this home also offers naturally extended views of the Withlacoochee forest directly behind, along with nearby trails, to further give you the peace, beautiful natural views, and seclusion you've only dreamt of!
